To run the program
In the terminal enter `javac BusRiderProblem.java`
Next run the compiled program by entering `java BusRiderProblem`

This program uses synchronization code that enforces all of the constraints in the Senate Bus Problem and will continue running until it is manually terminated.
Note that lines 114 and 118 of BusRiderProblem.java can be uncommented to print the waiting and boarding activity of each rider for better understanding.